[73.755472, "o", "                              \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m**Panic fix**:                                                                                                                                                                          \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- `renderMessageFull()` now clamps `YOffset` before calling `vp.View()` to prevent slice out-of-bounds                                                                                  \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- `resizeAll()` re-renders all messages for `allMessages` mode instead of calling `refreshMsgFullPreview()` which would replace content with a single message                           \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m                                       "]
[73.755514, "o", "                                                                                                                                                 \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m**Agent preview with fold/unfold**:                                                                                                                                                     \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- `buildAgentPreviewEntry()` loads agent messages and builds a synthetic `Entry` with a header block + all content blocks from all messages. This feeds into the same fold-aware        \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0mpreview system as regular messages.                                                                                                  "]
[73.755647, "o", "                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- Cache key uses `agent:{shortID}:{blockCount}` format for agent items                                                                                                                  \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- Removed the old plain-text `renderAgentSummary()` function                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                        \r\n                                         "]
