[77.587481, "o", "                                                                                                      \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- Uses `os.Lstat()` (no symlink follow) to get file info                                                                                                                                \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- Returns `true` if `.git` exists BUT is **NOT** a directory                                                                                                                            \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[38;2;56;189;248m│\u001b[0m- In a git worktree, `.git` is a file (not a directory) containing a reference to the actual `.git` directory                                                                   "]
